	* po-mode.el (po-mode) [po-XEMACS]: Explicitely add menus.
	Reported by Hrvoje Niksic.

	* po-mode.el (po-mode-menu-layout): Give real access to auxiliary
	files through the menu, instead of leaving menu entries inactive.

