	* gettext-sh: Initial revision.

	* elisp-comp:
	Use `rm -fr $tempdir' instead of `rm -f $tempdir/*; rmdir $tempdir'
	because some NFS implementation create .nfsxxx files which are
	not caught be the *.  Reported by Paul Nevai.

